title: MediationZone WebUI - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: The WebUI replaces the Desktop , and contains the same configuration, management, and monitoring UIs. It is a natively built web UI that complies to modern accessibility requirements. Open The WebUI. Please refer to the Desktop description for details on the sub-UIs.
